{"tid":470920,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"P牌遇著警岡","createTime":"2017-11-16T18:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T06:13:09.000Z","uid":157398,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"62f7548494be44b09c38af7741a62f7c3478c2d7","tid":470920,"uid":157398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:33:43.000Z","msg":"我大約一個月就脱P 但啱先發生左件事 係高速上遇到警岡 我下意識已經收慢架車 我見前面架車俾位啊sir用手電筒照完後就走得 我就慢慢向前行 我既注意放左係手電筒既光線 我本以為照完就走得 但慢行 一段小路就即刻俾位警員踢岀既雪糕筒截停 馬上被多位警員包圍 我較下車窗 <br />\n警察話我做咩衝岀黎 有冇飲酒 有冇被通緝 我馬上否認 我表示真係睇唔到有任何指示要我停車 年紀較大既警員就不斷質問我 做咩衝 (當時我車速慢 我冇踩油)我實話實說睇唔到  我亦接受左吹波仔 當然我冇飲酒 最後放左我走<br />\n其實我真係睇唔到佢有俾指示我停車 佢只係攞住個手電筒照  我只係想知道如果再遇到呢啲情況 我係咪應該垃低車窗 問佢冇問題先開車？"},{"pid":"c8b19178a1479fe826e0f81640c8bda0fc1a640a","tid":470920,"uid":13915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:45:02.000Z","msg":"停定，叫你走佢既會比手勢示意你走"},{"pid":"7f9b8a987d9924c9f6c15dd35c99424d1dee301b","tid":470920,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:47:13.000Z","msg":"鳩噏mode: <br />\n你見唔到佢有指示叫你停 <br />\n即係你都見唔到佢有指示叫你走喇 <br />\n正常情況佢check 完應該會畀signal 叫你走 <br />\n當你睇唔到佢signal 你走 <br />\n佢都應該會唔耐煩敲你窗<br />\n所以呢啲情況我估都係唔肯定走唔走得就停留原位安全啲"},{"pid":"0f2b4d5642c8cd16a75c8ba665ff544472f0ee6c","tid":470920,"uid":5150,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:50:00.000Z","msg":"有無人手拎一支橙紅色類似螢光棒嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n有嘅話垂直來回揮代表行得<br />\n<br />\n打橫代表要你停<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/024556_f462d94400017a6d7bb5083a49e95645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F024556_f462d94400017a6d7bb5083a49e95645.jpg&h=8a4370ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斜斜地指落地/隔離線或者斜斜地來回揮代表要你行側邊(左或右)<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/024659_57aecea79a4f37cba75486bfc576d196.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F024659_57aecea79a4f37cba75486bfc576d196.jpg&h=e5e6764a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4dd4e0cd1b638a9bc7a3f599dea95faea50d5e2","tid":470920,"uid":5150,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人手拎一支橙紅色類似螢光棒嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n有嘅話垂直來回揮代表行得<br />\n<br />\n打橫代表要你停<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/024556_f462d94400017a6d7bb5083a49e95645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F024556_f462d94400017a6d7bb5083a49e95645.jpg&h=8a4370ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斜斜地指落地/隔離線或者斜斜地來回揮代表要你行側邊(左或右)<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/024659_57aecea79a4f37cba75486bfc576d196.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F024659_57aecea79a4f37cba75486bfc576d196.jpg&h=e5e6764a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/025203_3919b038319e8a66ea4767ed9c52e1ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F025203_3919b038319e8a66ea4767ed9c52e1ae.jpg&h=25059410&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97a701c38cd7e5081b23a3ffc3f2874869c3ae31","tid":470920,"uid":48078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:53:37.000Z","msg":"較低車窗比佢照 照完跟拍示<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/024835_87565d85fb3158abe76037ae53ddd69d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F024835_87565d85fb3158abe76037ae53ddd69d.jpg&h=d0fdc063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/025325_69b45e7e86fea95b17c8009b9c053192.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F025325_69b45e7e86fea95b17c8009b9c053192.jpg&h=b1b13018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n埋位 入閘 起跑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5212fc94fc30e59e4c90919f3cc2a1a1221c0ac0","tid":470920,"uid":2467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:54:38.000Z","msg":"一定要停，除非佢比指示你走<br />\n<br />\n特別你p牌仔，有咩事停左係到先"},{"pid":"3eef17e19563f438a798da086e6673e87a261e0a","tid":470920,"uid":35173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:59:37.000Z","msg":"你唔知咪開窗問下呀sir係咪走得囉"},{"pid":"6a23af83b2b796415c516c207f3cc2dbebddad7c","tid":470920,"uid":46497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T19:19:05.000Z","msg":"一定有大大塊藍色牌寫住停車<br />\n你唔停告尻你都仲得"},{"pid":"59999cc598cb523bedd708e2252e65e7b809ce5f","tid":470920,"uid":103497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T20:56:59.000Z","msg":"不如你重新考過筆試"},{"pid":"7104f745a8d1d3e45b9c237d65938f00b08f2229","tid":470920,"uid":151774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T20:59:35.000Z","msg":"佢唔捉你埋去雞姦你咪偷笑囉"},{"pid":"7f34b0e296c3c55d538d57cb3ddc8bd6e570e3a0","tid":470920,"uid":13645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T21:03:24.000Z","msg":"地面擺左停車牌架柒頭"},{"pid":"d280cfa12fe14677465918c58c75581adccea141","tid":470920,"uid":37078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T21:12:03.000Z","msg":"你慢溜，去到佢度睇下佢有冇撥手叫你走先走，咁係最安全"},{"pid":"87296d82bae5eb09ae1d37e8c4ce6930e28890fe","tid":470920,"uid":70183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T21:26:02.000Z","msg":"基本上指示清晰到不得了<br />\n<br />\n您咁on9?"},{"pid":"50bafd84b0d695519cc5d38b5b34f5c9c496aceb","tid":470920,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T23:43:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地面擺左停車牌架柒頭</blockquote><br />\n正確答案。"},{"pid":"9504e927cf580227e5a8c79185dc2eb32367083c","tid":470920,"uid":5967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T23:56:55.000Z","msg":"你渣車望野焦點得一點嫁炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c660d2d9382f116bfc769c9a10e930091f9cba9","tid":470920,"uid":157398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T00:03:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人手拎一支橙紅色類似螢光棒嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n有嘅話垂直來回揮代表行得<br />\n<br />\n打橫代表要你停<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/024556_f462d94400017a6d7bb5083a49e95645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F024556_f462d94400017a6d7bb5083a49e95645.jpg&h=8a4370ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斜斜地指落地/隔離線或者斜斜地來回揮代表要你行側邊(左或右)<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/024659_57aecea79a4f37cba75486bfc576d196.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F024659_57aecea79a4f37cba75486bfc576d196.jpg&h=e5e6764a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢冇拎住支螢光棒 不過我以後會小心"},{"pid":"eff598788717ff64e6bb6b0fc53c7dd644d3bc0c","tid":470920,"uid":157398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T00:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳩噏mode: <br />\n你見唔到佢有指示叫你停 <br />\n即係你都見唔到佢有指示叫你走喇 <br />\n正常情況佢check 完應該會畀signal 叫你走 <br />\n當你睇唔到佢signal 你走 <br />\n佢都應該會唔耐煩敲你窗<br />\n所以呢啲情況我估都係唔肯定走唔走得就停留原位安全啲</blockquote><br />\n下次我會停到佢敲我窗"},{"pid":"5d7b957b3b3234e7351ed7c2f717536c227fad7d","tid":470920,"uid":157398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T00:05:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你渣車望野焦點得一點嫁炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係我大意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ea96e104ad41b09ba6f959132ea58d0382cb00","tid":470920,"uid":157398,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T00:10:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>較低車窗比佢照 照完跟拍示<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/024835_87565d85fb3158abe76037ae53ddd69d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F024835_87565d85fb3158abe76037ae53ddd69d.jpg&h=d0fdc063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/025325_69b45e7e86fea95b17c8009b9c053192.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F025325_69b45e7e86fea95b17c8009b9c053192.jpg&h=b1b13018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n埋位 入閘 起跑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為夜晚晚 我自己又第一次遇到警岡 佢只係拎住支手電 所以好光 我見佢照完放低 以為走  我下次會小心"},{"pid":"03430b6c0d28700385c6a6c55ccce27d87bcb89d","tid":470920,"uid":77811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T00:46:02.000Z","msg":"停咗先冇死"},{"pid":"7b07e359e892560203d9308a7415180069cde661","tid":470920,"uid":156893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我大約一個月就脱P 但啱先發生左件事 係高速上遇到警岡 我下意識已經收慢架車 我見前面架車俾位啊sir用手電筒照完後就走得 我就慢慢向前行 我既注意放左係手電筒既光線 我本以為照完就走得 但慢行 一段小路就即刻俾位警員踢岀既雪糕筒截停 馬上被多位警員包圍 我較下車窗 <br />\n警察話我做咩衝岀黎 有冇飲酒 有冇被通緝 我馬上否認 我表示真係睇唔到有任何指示要我停車 年紀較大既警員就不斷質問我 做咩衝 (當時我車速慢 我冇踩油)我實話實說睇唔到  我亦接受左吹波仔 當然我冇飲酒 最後放左我走<br />\n其實我真係睇唔到佢有俾指示我停車 佢只係攞住個手電筒照  我只係想知道如果再遇到呢啲情況 我係咪應該垃低車窗 問佢冇問題先開車？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你所講拎電筒條友側邊會有個停字牌<br />\n好人會打手號叫你停/行得<br />\n你飛蛾嚟？淨係見到支電筒啲光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n你算好彩，唔停可以告你無依照停字牌停車，無依照好人指示停車，仲可以告埋你不小心駕駛，你即刻可以報名排期等考多次車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d744bb7006a7e0f8291d2fbb33bb9645181b794","tid":470920,"uid":27017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:34:53.000Z","msg":"乜野警岡 <br />\nroadblock呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a327de4e9fa79139fc1adf890b3ec1fa3205e73d","tid":470920,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜野警岡 <br />\nroadblock呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要連崗都打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c34cb4e494bd972b1e48af3057dd8c1ac6659f","tid":470920,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"當年第一次過block都勁蝦碌<br />\n第一個差佬照完揮手叫我走<br />\n我行前有第二個差佬企正係路中心，但背住我，唔知搞乜<br />\n咁我諗住抽頭過佢啦 (而家諗返都幾痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n抽左三份一架車左右<br />\n四五個即刻差佬衝過黎㩒住我部車，狂喝我問我咩事，有啲仲有一隻手按實槍袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後停埋一邊死狗咁講sorry sir，以為走得，冇下次之類<br />\n問我一堆野，但又冇吹波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後見我個樣細路咁就放過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}